OL,3,CWords of heartbroken mother read out
OL,4,Cin Parliament in emotional speech by MP
OL,6,FThomas Cashman, the gunman who killed
OL,7,FOlivia as he chased a drug dealer who
OL,8,Fhad tried to run into her home in
OL,9,FKnotty Ash, Liverpool, did not appear
OL,10,Fto hear his life sentence in April
OL,11,F2023.
OL,13,FAs Ms Korbel watched tearfully from
OL,14,Fthe gallery, the Labour MP for
OL,15,FKnowsley praised her for her
OL,16,Fcampaigning on Olivia's law. Under the
OL,17,Flegislation, judges will be given the
OL,18,Fpower to sentence offenders for up to
OL,19,Ftwo more years in prison for avoiding
OL,20,Fjustice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
