OL,6,FFor offenders who already face lengthy
OL,7,Fimprisonment or whole life orders,
OL,8,Fjudges could also impose a range of
OL,9,Fprison punishments on offenders such
OL,10,Fas confinement to their cells and
OL,11,Fbeing stripped of privileges such as
OL,12,Fextra gym time.
OL,14,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,15,Fpromised to carry on the pledge to
OL,16,Fchange the law, first made by his
OL,17,Fpredecessor Rishi Sunak, when he met
OL,18,Fwith Ms Korbel in January this year.
