OL,3,CWords of heartbroken mother read out
OL,4,Cin Parliament in emotional speech by MP
OL,6,FThe measures are part of the Victims
OL,7,Fand Courts Bill, which had its second
OL,8,Freading in the Commons on Tuesday.
OL,10,FSpeaking during the debate, Ms Midgley
OL,11,Fsaid: "Today I speak to one part of
OL,12,Fthis Bill that will require convicted
OL,13,Foffenders to attend their sentence
OL,14,Fhearings and provide consequences
OL,15,Fwhere they refuse. It's known as
OL,16,FOlivia's law.
OL,26,@sD@GOU
