OL,3,CWords of heartbroken mother read out
OL,4,Cin Parliament in emotional speech by MP
OL,6,F"Olivia Pratt-Korbel was nine years
OL,7,Fold when she was murdered in her own
OL,8,Fhome, by a stranger with a gun. The
OL,9,Fmurderer, Thomas Cashman fired a
OL,10,Fbullet through the door of Olivia's
OL,11,Fhome, which passed through the wrist
OL,12,Fof my constituent, Cheryl Korbel,
OL,13,FOlivia's mother, before hitting Olivia
OL,14,Fin the chest and ending her life.
OL,16,F"Cheryl and her cousin Antonia are
OL,17,Fwith us in the chamber today.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
