OL,3,CWords of heartbroken mother read out
OL,4,Cin Parliament in emotional speech by MP
OL,6,F"Nothing in this world can bring
OL,7,FOlivia back, but instead of collapsing
OL,8,Funder this weight, Cheryl fought back.
OL,9,FShe and her family have campaigned so
OL,10,Fno other family would suffer the same.
OL,12,F"Olivia's law is her work, it's
OL,13,FOlivia's legacy, it's Cheryl's legacy.
OL,15,F"Today I will read out Cheryl's victim
OL,16,Fimpact statement. These are the words
OL,17,Fthe murderer, the coward Thomas
OL,18,FCashman refused to hear. I want the
OL,19,Fwords of Cheryl Korbel committed to
OL,20,Fthis House, so they will be on record
OL,21,Fin this place forever.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOU
