OL,3,CWords of heartbroken mother read out
OL,4,Cin Parliament in emotional speech by MP
OL,6,F"I cannot get my head around how
OL,7,FCashman continued to shoot after
OL,8,Fhearing the terrifying screams, the
OL,9,Futter devastation he has caused, he
OL,10,Fdoesn't care, how could he?
OL,12,F"His actions have left the biggest
OL,13,Fhole in our lives that can never be
OL,14,Ffilled. That man set out to do a job
OL,15,Fand he didn't care about anyone else
OL,16,For who got in the way. He certainly
OL,17,Fcouldn't own it either."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@XO]
