OL,6,FConcluding her speech, Ms Midgley
OL,7,Fsaid: "Let Cheryl's words be heard.
OL,8,FLet them be honoured. Let Olivia's law
OL,9,Fpass, and make sure that no victim's
OL,10,Fvoice is ever shut out of justice
OL,11,Fagain."
